metadata.name: Cat P #1
metadata.description:
The adventures of Cat P and his friends begin. 

I wandered the Internet and one day saw Pepe with ears! That's when the idea to create a pet cat was born. 

This cat is special. He has a lot of shenanigans, jokes and cuteness living in his head. There's also a little easterly trick, did you find it?

I donate a piece of my soul into each work, so that when you buy it you can touch my soul.
